title: Best ever carrot cake
ingredients: ['650g grated carrots', '220g dark brown soft sugar', '170g sultanas or raisins', '4 eggs', '300g caster sugar', '250ml vegetable oil', '2 teaspoons vanilla extract', '250g crushed pineapple, drained', '375g plain flour', '1 1/2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon salt', '4 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '120g chopped walnuts']
